snippet: Even with the Falcons at Denver, the perfect Vikings hosting Houston and the unbeaten Eagles returning from their bye to face Detroit, the spotlight is on Cleveland in Week 5. And no, the 0-4 Browns aren't the attraction. Tom Brady is....
lead_paragraph: Even with the Falcons at Denver, the perfect Vikings hosting Houston and the unbeaten Eagles returning from their bye to face Detroit, the spotlight is on Cleveland in Week 5. And no, the 0-4 Browns aren't the attraction. Tom Brady is.

headline.main: Here Comes Brady, as if Browns Don't Have Enough Problems
headline.print_headline: Here Comes Brady, as if Browns Don't Have Enough Problems
